Requirements:
  - X11 libraries and headers
  - structural get_opts (http://www.episec.com/people/edelkind/get_opts.html)


Compiling xgsk:

> curl -O http://episec.com/people/edelkind/arc/c/get_opts-current.tar.gz
> tar xvzf get_opts-current.tar.gz
> cd get_opts
> make
> cd ..
> gcc -o xgsk xgsk.c -O2 -s -Iget_opts -Lget_opts -lget_opts -lX11

Installing:

> sudo cp xgsk /usr/bin/

